import Project from '../models/Project';

export const PROJECTS = [
	new Project(
		1,
		'This website',
		'Website to show my skills, experiences, and projects',
		'Feel free to explore this website. Feedback is always more than welcome.',
		'React.js, SCSS, Node.js, JavaScript(ES6)',
		'Netlify',
		'3 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/sarah-alt-design',
		'',
		'https://res.cloudinary.com/seabysaltdesign/image/upload/q_auto/v1589302900/Images/ThisWebsite_xjqqo1.webp',
		'',
		'#FF5B3E',
		'#FF5B3E',
	),
	new Project(
		2,
		'Scenerie',
		'Platform to book weekend getaways in driving distance',
		'I was responsible for the whole frontend engineering and most of the design. I have worked on this project for a few months including different designs & iterations.',
		'React.js, Python, Flask, SCSS, Cloudinary, AWS, Google Analytics, Stripe, JavaScript(ES6)',
		'Netlify',
		'8 weeks',
		'https://github.com/florian-hartl/webapp',
		'https://youtu.be/A5Dk2LLKkCM',

		'#c4c3c3'
	),
	new Project(
		3,
		'Synapses',
		'Responsive memory game with different themes & levels',

		'Github Pages',
		'3 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/MemoryGame',
		'https://youtu.be/Vayfetaredc',
		'https://res.cloudinary.com/seabysaltdesign/image/upload/q_auto/v1589303764/Images/Synapses_new_cksknh.webp',
		'https://seabysalt.github.io/MemoryGame/',
		'#F8687F',
		'#F8687F',
	),
	new Project(
		4,
		'Marglas',

		'#E2F0FC',
		'#283170',
	),
	new Project(
		5,
		'Panthera',
